flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{One name argument?}
    B -- No --> C[Print usage and exit]
    B -- Yes --> D[Print input name]
    D --> E[Convert name to lowercase]
    E --> F[Save first letter as uppercase prefix]
    F --> G[Remove first letter from remaining name]
    G --> H[Map letters to Soundex digits]
    H --> I[Remove vowels and repeated digits]
    I --> J{First encoded group duplicates prefix group?}
    J -- Yes --> K[Drop duplicate leading digit]
    J -- No --> L[Keep suffix digits]
    K --> M[Append zero padding]
    L --> M
    M --> N[Take first four characters]
    N --> O[Print Soundex code]
    O --> P[Exit]
